If you find some bugs, please send us a detailed description of the
problem observed. Please include the logfile and a full description of
your setup.

To get a detailed log, use --verbose=7 and --logfile /var/log/tftpd to
generate a separate logfile. Please include the number of machines
that were booting of the server, the type of server (single or dual
processor, processor speed, etc.) and the type of network you have
(10Mbit, 100Mbit or 1Gbit).

Jean-Pierre Lefebvre <helix@step.polymtl.ca>
Remi Lefebvre <remi@step.polymtl.ca>